    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Okay, that makes sense. It sounds pretty risky. Are there any specific ways this clause could be interpreted that I should look out for? Like, are there any hidden loopholes or sneaky things in the wording that could make my liability even bigger than it looks at first glance?",
